headline: Wynn Resorts (NASDAQ:WYNN) Misses Q1 Revenue Estimates
summary: Luxury hotels and casino operator Wynn Resorts (NASDAQ:WYNN) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2025, with sales falling 8.7% year on year to $1.7 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.07 per share was 14% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
